r 4 days, he was slowly bleeding to death, one drop of mech fluid every few=
 minutes. He was warned about Maximal torture chambers. (He doesn't know th=
ey don't exist) He never knew they were as evil as this, though. Why do the=
 Maximals say that they aren't as hard as the Predacons? Anything would be =
better than this slow torture. But Gangon prayed to his lord Hell Beast tha=
t this would all be over soon...
